# .mvn/maven.config
# Threading configuration for parallel module builds
# 2C = 2 * CPU cores (24 threads on 12-core system)
# Maven builds are I/O-bound (file operations, network), so 2x cores allows better I/O overlap
# Tested: 2C (8.4s) > 1.5C (9.8s) > 1C (9.0s) for actor-service install
--threads=2C
-Dmaven.project.sourceRoots.warningsDisabled=true
